## [en] {Google / APP}

### [ App Title ] {google_description}

Classic Simple Old Maid

### [ Overview ] {google_description}

A classic Old Maid game where you compete for rank against three CPU players.

### [ App Description ] {all}

**Classic Simple Old Maid** is a simple Old Maid game where YOU (USER) take on CPU×3.

It uses standard Old Maid rules: draw one card from another player, match same-number pairs, and discard them.

The first player to run out of cards wins, and the player left holding the Joker at the end loses.

It also adds a **BET feature that uses in-game COIN**. Place a BET before the game starts and earn in-game COIN according to your rank.

This simple Old Maid was designed with a classic look, conceived and developed as an Old Maid game for adults.

### [ App Features ] {google_description / site_description}

* Designed for portrait play, comfortable to operate with one hand on a smartphone.
* Tuned to stay readable and easy to operate even on small phone screens.
* Supports Android 8 and later, running smoothly even on older Android devices.
* Special effects are reduced and optimized, so it stays light and smooth.

### [ Quick Start ] {quick_start_app}

* The dealer is decided at the start.
* Going clockwise, draw a card from the CPU on your left; the player still holding the Joker at the end loses.
* You can check the detailed rules in the guide.

### [ How to Play ] {guide_overview_app / site_description}

#### Steps

1. Decide your BET and tap [START]. Cards are dealt to the four players (52 cards plus one Joker).
2. Same-number pairs in your hand are automatically discarded to the center.
3. On your turn, draw one card from the next player's hand.
4. If the drawn card makes a pair, it is discarded right away.
5. When your hand is empty, you "finish." Players are ranked 1st, 2nd, 3rd, 4th in the order they finish.
6. The player still holding the Joker at the very end comes in last.

#### BET payout

* BET payout: 1st ×2.0 / 2nd ×1.5 / 3rd ×0.5 / 4th ×0
* If you BET 10 COIN: 20 / 15 / 5 / 0 COIN
* Fractions are rounded down (e.g., 5 ×0.5 = 2.5 → 2 COIN)
* No table fee is charged.
* BET rates are experimental and may change in future updates.

### [ In-App Purchases ] {google_description / guide_overview_app / site_description}

* Ads help us keep making and running the app. Thank you for understanding.
* An in-app purchase lets you hide ads and play offline (airplane mode, no-signal areas, and so on).
* Note: You still need the internet to update the app or open outside links.

### [ Notes ] {google_description / guide_overview_app / site_description}

* No real money, prizes, or crypto are used. This app is not for gambling.
* If the app feels slow, open Settings in the menu and clear the cache.
* If problems continue, delete the app's data in your device settings for a full reset.

### [ Supported Languages ] {google_description / site_description}

* English / Japanese / Chinese (Simplified)
- Note: Some words shown during play may be in English.

### [ Contact / Bug Report ] {guide_overview_app}

* To report a bug, use FEEDBACK on the game screen.
* If you need a reply, please use the [Contact form](https://app-flux-mirror.pages.dev/en/contact).

### [ Privacy Policy (External Link) ] {guide_overview_app}

* [Privacy policy link](https://app-flux-mirror.pages.dev/en/privacy-policy)



## [zh] {Google / APP}

### [ 应用标题 ] {google_description}

经典抽鬼牌 单机纸牌游戏

### [ 概述 ] {google_description}

一款采用经典设计的简单抽鬼牌纸牌游戏，与3名电脑玩家争夺排名。

### [ 应用说明 ] {all}

**Classic Simple Old Maid** 是一款由 YOU(USER) 对战 CPU×3 的简单抽鬼牌游戏。

采用标准的抽鬼牌规则：从其他玩家处抽取一张牌，凑成相同数字的对子并丢弃。

最先出完手牌即获胜，最后还拿着鬼牌则落败。

此外，新增了**使用游戏内 COIN 的 BET 功能**。游戏开始前先 BET，并根据名次获得游戏内 COIN。

这款简单的抽鬼牌采用经典设计，以面向成人的抽鬼牌为构想，精心设计并开发而成。

### [ 应用特点 ] {google_description / site_description}

* 专为竖屏游玩设计，单手握持手机也便于操作。
* 即使在小屏幕手机上，也调整得清晰易读、易于操作。
* 支持 Android 8 及以上，较旧的 Android 设备也能流畅运行。
* 已精简并优化特殊演出与特效，轻巧流畅。

### [ 快速上手 ] {quick_start_app}

* 开始时先决定庄家。
* 按顺时针方向，从左侧的 CPU 抽取手牌，最后还拿着鬼牌的人失败。
* 详细规则可在指南中查看。

### [ 玩法 ] {guide_overview_app / site_description}

#### 步骤

1. 决定 BET 后点击 [START]。给四位玩家发牌(52 张加 1 张鬼牌)。
2. 手牌中相同数字的对子会自动丢弃到中央。
3. 轮到你时，从下一位玩家的手牌中抽一张。
4. 抽到的牌若能凑成对子，就立刻丢弃。
5. 手牌清空即「完成」。按完成顺序排为 第1、第2、第3、第4。
6. 直到最后还拿着鬼牌的人，排在最后一名。

#### BET倍率

* BET倍率：第1名×2.0／第2名×1.5／第3名×0.5／第4名×0
* BET 10 COIN 时：20／15／5／0 COIN
* 小数部分向下取整(例：5×0.5＝2.5 → 2 COIN)
* 不收取台费。
* BET倍率为试验性设置，今后可能变更。

### [ 内购项目 ] {google_description / guide_overview_app / site_description}

* 广告能帮助我们持续制作和运营这款应用，感谢您的理解。
* 通过应用内购买，可隐藏广告并支持离线游玩(飞行模式、无信号的地方等)。
* 注：更新应用或打开外部链接时，仍需要联网。

### [ 注意事项 ] {google_description / guide_overview_app / site_description}

* 不使用任何现金、奖品或加密资产。本应用并非用于赌博。
* 如果运行变慢，请在菜单的设置中清除缓存。
* 如果仍有问题，可在设备设置中删除该应用的数据，恢复到初始状态。

### [ 支持语言 ] {google_description / site_description}

* 英语 / 日语 / 中文(简体)
- 注：游玩过程中的部分文字可能以英文显示。

### [ 联系我们 / 故障报告 ] {guide_overview_app}

* 报告故障，请使用游戏画面的 FEEDBACK。
* 如需回复，请通过 [Contact form](https://app-flux-mirror.pages.dev/zh/contact) 联系我们。

### [ 隐私政策(外部链接) ] {guide_overview_app}

* [Privacy policy link](https://app-flux-mirror.pages.dev/zh/privacy-policy)
